---
title: Roasted Broccoli Bengali Biryani with Currants & Roasted Almonds
description: Get ready for this bright, bold and beautiful meal that combines a touch of heat from aromatic spices with the sweetness of currants and the cooling flavours of mint and yoghurt. You'll be surprised at how easy it is to make this restaurant-quality dinner at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5f1f94bad4c0a238374bbf79-83507897.jpg
